original_title: PROGRESS Chapter 130: Dodge, Dip, Duck, Dive, Dodge
overview: PROGRESS Wrestling will be back at The Electric Ballroom in Camden, London on Sunday 20th March for Chapter 130: Dodge, Dip, Duck, Dive, Dodge. The main event is one for the ages as PROGRESS World Champion Cara Noir clashes with Ring Of Honor World Champion Jonathan Gresham in a title vs title match which will see one man guaranteed to walk out with two belts.
title: PROGRESS Chapter 130: Dodge, Dip, Duck, Dive, Dodge
